  ('locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-00414', 'locality-d0d1b9a2', 'locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-111-194ec0d9', 'sub-locality-d0d1b9a2-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關轉撥計價之敘述，下列敘述何者正確？', '["轉出部門有閒置產能時，按市價轉撥可能導致反功能決策", "轉出部門有閒置產能時，以全部成本為轉撥價格較不易導致反功能決策", "轉出部門無閒置產能時，應以轉出部門移轉之機會成本為最低移轉價格", "轉出部門無閒置產能時，以實際成本為轉撥價格會使轉出部門致力於成本控制"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2b0bca06b571", "answer_pdf_sha1": "383f703f9d9c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111190", "c": "315", "s": "1505", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "成本與管理會計", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-00415', 'locality-d0d1b9a2', 'locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-111-194ec0d9', 'sub-locality-d0d1b9a2-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲公司計畫購買線性滑軌工具機，成本$210,000，估計耐用年限 8 年，無殘值，採直線法折 舊。預期每年可產生稅前現金流入$50,000，所得稅率為20%，下列何者為此工具機購買之回 收期限？（四捨五入取至小數點後第2位）', '["3.44年", "3.80年", "4.64年", "5.25年"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2b0bca06b571", "answer_pdf_sha1": "383f703f9d9c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111190", "c": "315", "s": "1505", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "成本與管理會計", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-00416', 'locality-d0d1b9a2', 'locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-111-194ec0d9', 'sub-locality-d0d1b9a2-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '居家檢疫住房客人因新型冠狀病毒前後交叉感染而確診，甲防疫旅館為解決室內交叉感染問 題導入平衡計分卡，要求「有效縮短清潔時間並提升清潔服務品質」並以其為重要績效指標， 此指標應歸類為何種構面？', '["財務構面", "顧客構面", "內部流程構面", "學習與成長構面"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2b0bca06b571", "answer_pdf_sha1": "383f703f9d9c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111190", "c": "315", "s": "1505", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "成本與管理會計", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-00417', 'locality-d0d1b9a2', 'locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-111-194ec0d9', 'sub-locality-d0d1b9a2-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲公司為輪胎製造商，價值鏈中依序發生下列成本：品管訓練$5,500，採購零件檢查$2,800， 產品試製$2,500，設計階段產品耐用度測試$6,000，產品成分檢查$5,200，生產階段產品耐用 度測試$5,000，瑕疵產品廢棄$12,000，瑕疵品重製$8,000，顧客抱怨處理$3,600，產品維修運 費$2,600，產品傷害賠償$18,500。下列何者為甲公司的預防成本？', '["$11,500", "$14,000", "$16,800", "$19,000"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2b0bca06b571", "answer_pdf_sha1": "383f703f9d9c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111190", "c": "315", "s": "1505", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "成本與管理會計", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 25, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-00418', 'locality-d0d1b9a2', 'locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-111-ac2adf20', 'sub-locality-d0d1b9a2-02', NULL, 'essay', '某政府上年度年底之會計紀錄顯示歲出共610億元，投資民營事業15億
