經常支出金額。
非屬歲出之支出有那幾項及其金額合計。', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:09+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "91c2d8a44a43", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111190", "c": "315", "s": "1507", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "政府會計", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-00419', 'locality-d0d1b9a2', 'locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-111-ac2adf20', 'sub-locality-d0d1b9a2-02', NULL, 'essay', '回答下列有關政府會計觀念公報及政府會計準則公報之相關問題：
